## High-level description
This file defines feature flags and their values for the `production` namespace. It is a YAML file used for testing purposes.

## Symbols
There are no symbols in this file as it is a data file in YAML format.

## Configuration
This file defines a single configuration option:

| Option    | Type   | Default | Description                                  |
| :-------- | :----- | :------- | :------------------------------------------- |
| namespace | string | N/A      | The namespace for the defined feature flags |

The file then lists feature flags and their values within this namespace. The specific flags and values are not included in the provided snippet.
